# Social Sharing

## Features
- Implement on results page using @components/SocialShare.tsx.
- Include share buttons for:
  - WhatsApp.
  - X (Twitter).
  - Facebook.
- Shared content includes:
  - Test title.
  - Test link.
  - Time taken.
  - Score.
- Display a rating component for user feedback.

## Best Practices
- Use shadcn/ui for buttons and rating component.
- Ensure share links are properly encoded.
- Test sharing functionality to be responsive on mobile and desktop.